TOSIBOX® eliminates 2 major hurdles to IIoT enablement: the risk associated with security and the lack of budget to purchase and maintain highly complex security solutions. The Lock 500i is a ruggedized, industrial, intelligent, network agnostic, failover capable, secure instant connectivity appliance used with the TOSIBOX® platform for customers that just want a VZW 4G SIM card and instant encrypted connectivity in seconds. The Lock 500i provides massive VPN throughput for any high bandwidth, high speed, low latency application or use case. The Lock 500iC is both cellular and ethernet capable on the WAN side. The Lock 500i is also ethernet and wi-fi capable on the LAN side. TOSIBOX® allows individual users or user groups (unlimited) instant remote access to any connected asset behind every lock at any time for continuous monitoring, network maintenance, network management or real time data collection via simple drag and drop. TOSIBOX® speeds up 5G adoption, as there can be legacy devices across many different technologies to connect and TOSIBOX® brings them all together.
